==English==
===Etymology===
''[[Proto]]-'' + ''[[science]]''

=== Noun ===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# an unscientific field of study which later becomes a science (e.g. astrology becoming astronomy and alchemy becoming chemistry). 
# a field of study which appears to conform to the scientific method but is not falsifiable, or if it is, its predictions have not yet been observed.